# AI playtesting guard (manual only)

## Critical rule

Never launch browser tools, open localhost, navigate the game, or take screenshots unless the user **explicitly** asks to playtest.

## Disallowed without a clear request

- “Let me verify in the browser”
- “I’ll open the game to check”
- Proactive browser validation after edits

## Allowed when the user asks

Phrases like: **playtest**, **test in browser**, **open the game**, **screenshot**, **verify in game**.

## Procedure

Follow `.cursor/commands/playtest.md`. Prefer any **project-documented** automation hooks over guessing UI flows.
